General
=======

* make scripts run with a lcdf typetools version > 2.69
* fix generation of dotless j
* the font scaling option is not taken into account when determining
  the (optical) weight; fix that


Myriad Pro
==========

* accent positions of mathrm letters
* kerning
* integrals including integral from Myriad Pro fonts
* adaptation of MnSymbols


Cronos Pro
==========

* some kind of math support
* kerning
* clean up of CronosPro.dtx
